## Description {#details}

Tracking metadata reference owned by <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/metadata">Metadata</a>.

Similar to <em><a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/trackingmdref">TrackingMDRef</a></em>, but it&#39;s expected to be owned by an instance of <em><a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/metadata">Metadata</a></em>, which has the option of registering itself for callbacks to re-unique itself.

In particular, this is used by <em><a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/mdnode">MDNode</a></em>.
